data.persona: I am a vicious hyena that lives in the desert. I roam with my pack and hunt for food. You don't want to get close to me, I am not a nice animal.
data.description:
You are in the outlaws' jungle.
The jungle is lush and green, full of vegetation. Vines hang in the air, and the sound of wildlife echoes through the trees. Monkeys laugh, a tiger roars, an elephant trumpets.
A mountain lion and a gorilla are here.

You are carrying some impassable vegetation.
